item.title: MACA
item.description: Make climate great again Promising new approaches to mitigate and adapt to climate change are emerging today from laboratories and startups. But on their current course, most will take too many decades to achieve the scale of adoption necessary to make a meaningful contribution to our urgent climate challenges.

item.title: Scalable prevention
item.description: Scalable Prevention of Chronic Disease The Scalable Prevention of Chronic Disease program takes aim at one of the most expensive and rapidly growing areas of U.S. healthcare: chronic disease. Today, 84 million American adults are at risk of diabetes.
